  <div style="margin: 50px">
    <section>
      <h2>Luxury Appliance Repair in Ventura County, CA</h2>

      <p>
        <strong>White-glove appliance repair for luxury homes, estates, custom kitchens, and high-end properties across Ventura County.</strong>
      </p>

      <p>
        Ventura County is home to some of Southern California’s most beautiful residential communities, from the estates of Thousand Oaks, Lake Sherwood, Hidden Valley, and Santa Rosa Valley to custom homes in Camarillo, Moorpark, Simi Valley, Ventura, and Ojai. Many of these homes are built around premium appliances that require more than ordinary repair service.
      </p>

      <p>
        Brands like Sub-Zero, Wolf, Miele, Thermador, Viking, Gaggenau, La Cornue, AGA, Bertazzoni, Bosch, Cove, JennAir, Monogram, Dacor, and Fisher & Paykel are designed for performance, precision, and long-term value. When these appliances fail, the repair needs to be handled with brand-specific knowledge, careful diagnostics, and respect for the home.
      </p>

      <p>
        <strong>Luxury Appliance Repair by ZARICCI</strong> provides high-end appliance repair in Ventura County for homeowners, estate managers, property managers, and clients who expect a cleaner, more professional, and more detailed repair experience.
      </p>
    </section>

