      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>Luxury Appliance Brand Experience</strong><br />
          We focus on high-end and European appliance brands including Sub-Zero, Wolf, Miele, Thermador, Viking, Gaggenau, La Cornue, AGA, Lacanche, Bertazzoni, Fulgor Milano, ILVE, Bosch, Cove, JennAir, Monogram, Dacor, Fisher & Paykel, True Residential, and Signature Kitchen Suite.
        </li>

        <li>
          <strong>Service for Built-In and Custom Kitchen Appliances</strong><br />
          Many Ventura County homes feature panel-ready refrigeration, built-in wine cooling, professional ranges, double ovens, steam ovens, smart kitchen appliances, and integrated cabinetry. We understand how to service these systems carefully.
        </li>

        <li>
          <strong>Same-Day and Priority Appointments When Available</strong><br />
          We offer convenient scheduling for Ventura County customers, including same-day and next-day availability when the schedule allows.
        </li>

        <li>
          <strong>White-Glove Service Inside High-Value Homes</strong><br />
          We protect floors, cabinetry, panels, counters, and surrounding finishes while maintaining a clean and respectful work area.
        </li>

        <li>
          <strong>Clear Communication and Upfront Repair Recommendations</strong><br />
          After diagnosis, we explain the issue, the recommended repair, parts needs, and estimated cost before moving forward.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h3>High-End Appliances We Repair in Ventura County</h3>

      <h4>Luxury Refrigerator and Freezer Repair</h4>

      <p>
        We repair built-in refrigerators, column refrigerators, freezer drawers, integrated refrigeration systems, undercounter units, and luxury cooling appliances from Sub-Zero, Thermador, Miele, Viking, Monogram, True Residential, Fisher & Paykel, Gaggenau, and other premium brands.
      </p>

      <ul>
        <li>Refrigerator not cooling properly</li>
        <li>Freezer temperature problems</li>
        <li>Ice maker not producing ice</li>
        <li>Water dispenser failure</li>
        <li>Excess frost, condensation, or moisture buildup</li>
        <li>Compressor, evaporator fan, condenser fan, sensor, and control board issues</li>
        <li>Door seal, hinge, and custom panel alignment problems</li>
      </ul>

      <h4>Luxury Range, Oven, Stove, and Cooktop Repair</h4>

      <p>
        We service professional cooking appliances from Wolf, Viking, Thermador, Gaggenau, La Cornue, AGA, Bertazzoni, ILVE, Fulgor Milano, BlueStar, Hestan, Dacor, Monogram, and other luxury cooking brands.
      </p>

      <ul>
        <li>Burners not igniting</li>
        <li>Oven not heating</li>
        <li>Uneven baking or roasting</li>
        <li>Gas burner clicking or delayed ignition</li>
        <li>Induction cooktop error codes</li>
        <li>Control panel, relay board, sensor, thermostat, and ignition problems</li>
        <li>Door, hinge, gasket, and calibration issues</li>
      </ul>

      <h4>Premium Dishwasher Repair</h4>

      <p>
        We repair high-end dishwashers from Miele, Bosch, Cove, Thermador, Fisher & Paykel, Viking, JennAir, and other premium dishwasher brands installed in luxury kitchens throughout Ventura County.
      </p>

      <ul>
        <li>Dishwasher not draining</li>
